headline: Freeport-McMoRan (FCX) Valuation Check After Earnings And Copper Demand Optimism
summary: Freeport-McMoRan (FCX) is back in focus after reporting fourth quarter and full year 2025 results, with sales of US$5,633 million for the quarter and US$25,915 million for the year. See our latest analysis for Freeport-McMoRan. The latest earnings release comes after a sharp run in the stock, with a 24.53% 1 month share price return and a 60.83% 3 month share price return.
